Orbis,is,a,provider,of,secure,electronic,trading,systems,for,the,global,financial,industry,With,Orbis,solutions,users,have,access,to,markets,with,real,time,quotes,rapid,execution,times,and,tools,to,help,manage,their,portfolio,and,evaluate,market,trends,Orbis,provides,a,fast,trading,API,for,use,by,automated,traders,The,API,provides,real,time,market,access,and,includes,customizable,risk,management,tools,to,prevent,over,buying,and,over,selling,of,shares,as,well,as,a,live,monitoring,feature,that,allows,users,to,track,the,progress,of,their,trades,and,get,real,time,P,L,information,Interested,developers,should,contact,the,provider,for,more,information